{"type": "article", "id": 61824, "title": "可持续包装成了潮流，这套个护产品的包装看起来不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-06T23:08:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 57112, "name": "BREUER"}, {"id": 1277, "name": "IKEA"}, {"id": 57113, "name": "Flexform"}, {"id": 8926, "name": "Tom Dixon"}, {"id": 52738, "name": "Joel Escalona"}, {"id": 57114, "name": "Antonio Citterio"}, {"id": 57115, "name": "Elena Amato"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 151, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190306212529xskWIezYSDwr24uX.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><h3>The Sustainable Cosmetics Packaging From Bacteria by Elena Amato </h3><p>危地马拉设计师 Elena Amato 创造了具有纸质特性的细菌纤维素薄片，作为个人护理产品中使用的塑料包装的可持续替代品。</p><p>她使用水、细菌和酵母培养物的混合物培养细菌纤维素片，将其混合在一起，然后展开在平坦、光滑的表面上并使其干燥。</p><p>最终制成的材料质感介于纸张和塑料之间，干燥的细菌纤维素材料可以使用水粘合在一起，从而在密封包装时不需要使用胶水或其他粘合剂。</p><p>在混合过程中，设计师将天然色素如螺旋藻、木槿、藏红花和木炭加入混合物中以获得不同的颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212602ncq9ZU4Yx5wrdjeV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212601X4IcD2rfQmSsvBgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212602RfP7wH3gYTz8MLt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212603Thj1RkVLFMAvtZqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212603IAW86H7iVjul0StX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212603EZb7KIFnxa0gCsNQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212603ARfL0lqGs3boMvQg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212627L7VP9W4XjEbFyzMf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/02/28/elena-amato-bacteria-packaging-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The New Collection by Antonio Citterio for Flexform</h3><p>米兰设计师 Antonio Citterio 为意大利品牌 Flexform 创造了一系列家具，意在满足日常生活的实用性。</p><p>这个系列包括沙发、扶手椅、餐椅、咖啡桌和几个配件，围绕尽可能实用和对用户友好的原则来设计。“每个 Flexform 产品与众不同之处在于它易于识别，为日常使用而设计，并且易于使用，” Citterio 说。</p><p>Campiello 组合沙发具有精美的形状和鹅绒填充垫，意在“放大柔软包裹的感觉”。Leda 扶手椅有一个木质底座，带有有角度的靠背和圆形带衬垫的座椅，分为低靠背或高靠背两种。</p><p>Hera 椅子和扶手椅有一个圆形的软垫座椅和一个弧形靠背。Ascanio Occasional 咖啡桌采用木质结构和圆形表面，有木质或大理石桌面可供选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212729dmKIlSfA5oWbj1xz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.155245\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212705emr2dhTfA8WSpVQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062127057PSDFM1Hcq9jZ8Ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526650\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212707OvXp9DiSMrB6nmgN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.flexform.it/en/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flexform</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Överallt furniture collection by IKEA &amp; top African designers</h3><p>最近，宜家将会推出与非洲顶级设计师合作的 Överallt 家具系列，这也是宜家首个非洲设计系列，这些产品预计将于今年 5 月份在全球各地的商店推出。</p><p>整个系列在开普敦的 Design Indaba 亮相，包括来自 5 个非洲国家的创意产品，宜家希望通过该项目能够向全世界展示非洲现在正在涌现的创造力。</p><p>塞内加尔艺术家 Selly Raby Kane 设计了一个看起来像编织头发的篮子，有两种尺寸，由纺织纤维制成，看起来像编织头发。</p><p>埃及女设计师 Mariam Hazem 和 Hend Riad 改造了宜家的经典款蓝黄色购物袋 FRAKTA，她们利用废弃的薯片包装袋和黄麻纤维为原材料来制作新版的 FRAKTA 购物袋，质感比原来的塑料袋更加厚实。</p><p>科特迪瓦设计师 Issa Diabaté 设计了一把简单的椅子，反映了非洲户外和室内生活方式。该椅子仅使用一张胶合板制成，可根据用户的需求进行定制。</p><p>南非时装设计师 Laduma Ngxokolo 则结合非洲南部科萨族的文化，与宜家设计师 Mikael Axelsson 合作设计了一款规则几何图案的地毯。</p><p>设计师 Naeem Biviji 和 Bethan Rayner 创造了一系列专为灵活烹饪和用餐而设计的产品，包括一个可与其他人组合在一起的凳子和长凳，带有盖子的铸铁盘，可作为煎锅和三个软木锅架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212820WawF9zgdu1rjGyYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799915\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212821l81a4cyA23hLqWpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212827LYBCjopUP92QrR7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212828lsGIX7Q4JhgFMwpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212830k9sCJH3Wng862zhL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212829FeZ9JuRWLwkSPa0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062128262oiMr76G1aRXgSZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212830NDMrTVGxSCvkcbdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212830e2SuGT6rQU0qCRmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212836mEphF7YlxqoSMHD9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Laws of Motion by Joel Escalona for BREUER</h3><p>Laws of Motion 是墨西哥设计师 Joel Escalona 为家具和定制室内设计公司 BREUER 制作的第一个收藏品系列。这一系列包括椅子、隔断、餐桌、凳子、长凳、镜子、咖啡、边桌以及橱柜。</p><p>Laws of Motion 系列每件作品都结合了橡木、大理石和金属等精雕细琢的材料结果，试图在优雅和复杂的结构之间取得平衡。设计师试图探索重力和运动等概念，也希望能够给用户一些思考和启发。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030621291212z8IcKX9OZrlDbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062129123TfmroANjJ6kuhOa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062129139JZXsFDVuWqj7lBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212912mojK1y6MigOpnQu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062129130PyCY2exdDXmpQS9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212913nmE0UjI17b4AiFfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://joelescalona.com/lawsofmotion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joel Escalona</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>FAT Chair Series by Tom Dixon</h3><p>英国工业设计师 Tom Dixon 最新推出 FAT 系列椅子，简约美学搭配幽默放松的轮廓设计，整个系列均由经验丰富的工匠手工完成，能作为餐椅、吧台椅、休闲椅等实用，像是拥抱着你的各种坐姿，给人温暖又绅士的感觉。</p><p>模压泡沫垫和高光泽黑色漆金属制成的腿部，衬托出简洁利落的线条。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212950lBYqwRC26P87aN5h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212950cWTyRh5ptjnqAelU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212950L7fqeEsjTRtwDu9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212950FMrxLW5Ai71B9aEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306212950uxe9Mhki8ZX20G1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.270312\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062129504ps23q9VFP7DGkyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903062129515kLlXQRzxtofT9US.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.570313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/tom-dixon-a-fat-chair-series-that-will-cuddle-you/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}